</paragraph>
<paragraph id="725E36EC2494BDCDFF66DF8F1E5CA135" blockId="138.[151,1438,152,603]" pageId="138" pageNumber="139">
<emphasis id="4095EAFE2494BDCDFF66DF8F1A80A2E6" bold="true" box="[198,447,461,487]" pageId="138" pageNumber="139">Taxonomic notes:—</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="B5E14D6F2494BDCDFE1FDF8F19A0A2E6" authorityName="Grayum &amp; de Nevers" authorityYear="1988" box="[447,671,461,487]" class="Liliopsida" family="Arecaceae" genus="Geonoma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Arecales" pageId="138" pageNumber="139" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="scoparia">
<emphasis id="4095EAFE2494BDCDFE1FDF8F19A0A2E6" box="[447,671,461,487]" italics="true" pageId="138" pageNumber="139">Geonoma scoparia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is closely related to 
<taxonomicName id="B5E14D6F2494BDCDFC34DF8F1F15A2E6" authorityName="de Nevers &amp; Grayum" authorityYear="1995" box="[916,1066,461,487]" class="Liliopsida" family="Arecaceae" genus="Geonoma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Arecales" pageId="138" pageNumber="139" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="mooreana">
<emphasis id="4095EAFE2494BDCDFC34DF8F1F15A2E6" box="[916,1066,461,487]" italics="true" pageId="138" pageNumber="139">G. mooreana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, the two species differing from related species (the 
<taxonomicName id="B5E14D6F2494BDCDFE20DFB61AD4A10F" authorityName="Henderson, Borchsenius &amp; Balslev" authorityYear="2008" box="[384,491,500,526]" class="Liliopsida" family="Arecaceae" genus="Geonoma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Arecales" pageId="138" pageNumber="139" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="lanata">
<emphasis id="4095EAFE2494BDCDFE20DFB61AD4A10F" box="[384,491,500,526]" italics="true" pageId="138" pageNumber="139">G. lanata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
clade) in their proximal and distal lips joined to form a raised cupule. 
<taxonomicName id="B5E14D6F2494BDCDFA8ADFB61BC1A134" authorityName="Grayum &amp; de Nevers" authorityYear="1988" class="Liliopsida" family="Arecaceae" genus="Geonoma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Arecales" pageId="138" pageNumber="139" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="scoparia">
<emphasis id="4095EAFE2494BDCDFA8ADFB61BC1A134" italics="true" pageId="138" pageNumber="139">Geonoma scoparia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
differs from 
<taxonomicName id="B5E14D6F2494BDCDFE38DC581911A134" authorityName="de Nevers &amp; Grayum" authorityYear="1995" box="[408,558,538,565]" class="Liliopsida" family="Arecaceae" genus="Geonoma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Arecales" pageId="138" pageNumber="139" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="mooreana">
<emphasis id="4095EAFE2494BDCDFE38DC581911A134" box="[408,558,538,565]" italics="true" pageId="138" pageNumber="139">G. mooreana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in its solitary stems and internodes covered with dense, brown scales.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="725E36EC2494BDCDFF66DC031E65A15A" blockId="138.[151,1438,152,603]" box="[198,1370,577,603]" pageId="138" pageNumber="139">
<emphasis id="4095EAFE2494BDCDFF66DC031ACBA15A" bold="true" box="[198,500,577,603]" pageId="138" pageNumber="139">Subspecific variation:—</emphasis>
No trait varies within this species nor is there any geographic disjunction.
</paragraph>
